high_descs: Turn left and then walk forward to the bath tub.
Pick up the soap from the bath tub.
Turn left then turn right with the bar of soap.
Place the bar of soap in the bath tub.
Turn completely around and then turn left to face the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink and take out a bar of soap.
Turn around and walk to the left back to the bath tub.
Place the bar of soap in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn left and face the tub in front of you.
Take the soap from the tub in front of you.
Turn right, then face the tub on your right.
Place the soap in the tub in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink on your left.
Open the cabinet under the sink in front of you and take out another bar of soap, close the cabinet.
Turn left and face the tub in front of you.
Place the bar of soap in the tub in front of you.
Turn left at the sink and walk to the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap on the edge of the tub.
Move over to the left side of the tub.
Place the bar of soap in the tub in front of the drain.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left side.
Open the cabinet on the right side under the sink, pick up the bar of soap, close the door.
Turn and walk to the tub.
Put the bar of soap down in the tub to the left of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the tub.
